Package: dmj-vault-apps-api
Architecture: all
Depends: ${python3:Depends}, ${misc:Depends},
         python3-fastapi,
         python3-uvicorn,
         gunicorn,
         nginx,
         dmj-vault-dbaccess
Description: FastAPI /check endpoint for dmj-vault
 Validates API keys against the DMJ_VAULT database, checking key
 validity, expiry, optional IP whitelist, and permission scopes.
 Runs under gunicorn (uvicorn workers) on 127.0.0.1:9702, exposed
 via nginx on 127.0.0.1:9800 by default.
